It scares me to think what would have happened if you weren't there, Vidia.
维蒂亚 如果你不在旁边 还不知道会发生什么呢

550
00:49:33,530 --> 00:49:35,470
I don't know what to say.
我不知道说什么好

551
00:49:35,530 --> 00:49:39,270
- How about faith... - Trust...
- 来一个 信念... - 信任...

552
00:49:39,610 --> 00:49:40,940
- And ... - And ...
- 还有...

553
00:49:41,040 --> 00:49:43,010
And pixie dust.
还有仙粉

554
00:49:43,140 --> 00:49:45,130
And pixie dust!
还有仙粉!

555
00:49:45,210 --> 00:49:46,640
Can you reach it, Clanky?
你够得着吗 柯朗?

556
00:49:47,950 --> 00:49:50,780
- Almost. Just a little more. - Here, let me.
- 就要够着了只差一点点 - 我来了

557
00:49:51,620 --> 00:49:53,950
Okay. Now, can you see anything?
好了 现在 你能看见了吗?

558
00:49:54,190 --> 00:49:57,450
No! There's a big building in the way.
不行! 被一个大建筑物挡住了

559
00:49:57,990 --> 00:50:03,050
Building. It's a house. That's it! Clanky! We've got it!
建筑物 是一座房子 那就对了 柯朗 我们到了!

560
00:50:03,160 --> 00:50:05,390
- What've we got? - House! Get off.
- 到什么地方了? - 房子 下来

561
00:50:05,500 --> 00:50:07,730
- I'm sorry. - I can't feel my legs.
- 对不起 - 我的腿没知觉了

562
00:50:12,470 --> 00:50:17,700
It doesn't matter what I say. He never believes me.
不管我说什么 他都不相信我

563
00:50:19,680 --> 00:50:21,480
I'm so sorry, Lizzy.
我真抱歉 莉兹

564
00:50:24,750 --> 00:50:26,720
I'm so glad you're here.
真高兴你在这里

565
00:50:27,990 --> 00:50:29,850
You're my best friend.
你是我最好的朋友

566
00:50:37,430 --> 00:50:40,490
I wish I were a fairy, just like you.
我真想变成一个仙子 就像你一样

567
00:50:42,170 --> 00:50:45,230
Then I could help the flowers bloom and talk to animals
那样我就可以让花开放 还可以和动物说话

568
00:50:45,340 --> 00:50:48,570
and fly around with the other fairies all the time.
还可以整天和别的仙子们一起飞

569
00:50:53,850 --> 00:50:55,510
