那多么快乐呀

570
00:51:07,390 --> 00:51:09,120
Where are we going?
我们去哪里?

571
00:52:12,120 --> 00:52:13,990
What is going on up there?
上面在干什么呢?

572
00:52:29,140 --> 00:52:31,630
I was going to present it to the museum ton ght.
我今晚要在博物馆展示

573
00:52:31,710 --> 00:52:33,540
Now the butterfly is gone.
可是现在蝴蝶跑了

574
00:52:56,240 --> 00:53:01,200
Oh, my! I'm... I'm flying!
噢! 天呀 我...我在飞了!

575
00:53:05,080 --> 00:53:09,070
Look at me! Whee! I'm a fairy!
看我 哎 我是仙子了

576
00:53:19,590 --> 00:53:20,920
All clear!
安全!

577
00:53:26,570 --> 00:53:27,930
- Sorry. - Oh! Careful.
- 对不起 - 噢! 当心

578
00:53:28,030 --> 00:53:29,230
- That's my ear - Sorry.
- 那是我的耳朵 - 对不起

579
00:53:29,330 --> 00:53:30,700
- Sorry. - That's the nose Careful.
- 对不起 - 那是鼻子 小心

580
00:53:30,770 --> 00:53:32,430
- Whoops! Sorry. - Can't see!
- 呜! 抱歉 - 我看不见了

581
