Okay. Tinker Bell is upstairs. The little girl has her in a cage.
好的 叮当在楼上 那女孩把她装在笼子里

582
00:53:36,440 --> 00:53:38,030
In a cage?
装在笼子里?

583
00:53:38,110 --> 00:53:40,010
And there's also a large human in the house
这个房子里还有一个大的人类

584
00:53:40,080 --> 00:53:44,670
who doesn't like creatures with wings. He pins them up in display cases.
他不喜欢长翅膀的生物 他把它们钉在展示盒里

585
00:53:45,450 --> 00:53:49,180
- Great. Anything else? - Oh, yes. The cat
- 太好了 还有别的吗? - 噢 还有 那只猫

586
00:53:49,350 --> 00:53:51,020
Cat! What cat?
猫! 什么猫?

587
00:53:51,590 --> 00:53:53,350
- That cat! - That cat!
- 就是那个猫! - 就是那个猫!

588
00:53:57,530 --> 00:54:01,190
Fawn, you're an animal fairy. What are we supposed to do?
芳纹 你是动物仙子呀 我们能怎么做?

589
00:54:03,140 --> 00:54:05,190
- Fawn? - Fly!
- 芳纹? ! - 飞!

590
00:54:05,270 --> 00:54:06,260
Our wings are wet.
我们的翅膀都是湿的

591
00:54:06,370 --> 00:54:07,700
And who knows when they'll be dry.
谁知道什么时候才能干

592
00:54:07,770 --> 00:54:09,600
Okay, okay. Run!
好的 好的 快跑!

593
00:54:22,390 --> 00:54:24,410
- Clank! - Come on!
- 柯朗! - 加油!

594
00:54:28,830 --> 00:54:32,230
- Clank! - I'm okay.
- 柯朗! - 我没事

595
00:54:33,930 --> 00:54:36,800
We still need to get to that stairwell. Any ideas?
我们还是要到那楼梯间去 有办法吗?

596
00:54:36,900 --> 00:54:38,890
If we could just build a brdge or something
也许我们架一座桥 或别的什么

597
00:54:38,970 --> 00:54:41,910
- That's it. A bridge! - Guys? Guys?
- 对 一座桥! - 伙计们? 伙计们?

598
00:54:42,070 --> 00:54:44,440
- A bridge made out of what? - Guys!
- 用什么造桥呢? - 伙计们!

599
00:54:46,310 --> 00:54:48,300
Clank! You're a genius!
柯朗! 你真是天才!

600
00:54:48,750 --> 00:54:50,270
Huh? Uh.
呃? 噢

601
00:54:52,450 --> 00:54:53,750
It was nothing.
这不算什么

602
00:54:56,790 --> 00:54:58,980
All right. Let's do this.
好吧 我们干吧

603
00:55:08,670 --> 00:55:13,100
- We need some more plates! - Okay. Start passing them up Clanky.
- 我们还要些盘子 - 好的 柯朗把盘子递过来

604
00:55:13,510 --> 00:55:16,960
Aye, aye! Here they come!
是! 这就来了!

605
00:55:20,110 --> 00:55:22,960
Get ready for more. Oh, hello!
准备接着收货 呃...哈喽!

606
00:55:24,850 --> 00:55:26,940
We've got a full plate back here!
盘子够了!

607
00:55:27,050 --> 00:55:30,720
No, no, no. No. No, please.
不 不 不 请别过来

608
00:55:31,160 --> 00:55:32,150
Get back!
回去!

609
00:55:46,910 --> 00:55:48,000
Get back!
回去!

610
00:55:48,070 --> 00:55:51,170
Rosetta! Is this what I think it is?
萝瑟塔! 这就是我想要的东西吗?

611
00:55:51,640 --> 00:55:54,840
That is exactly what you think it is. Catnip!
对了 这正是你要的 猫薄荷!

612
00:55:55,480 --> 00:55:58,010
You get to Tink and we'll take care of the cat!
你去找叮当 我们来对付猫!

613
00:55:58,080 --> 00:55:59,070
Got it!
明白

614
00:56:17,240 --> 00:56:19,330
- Lizzy? - Coming, Father!
- 莉兹? - 请进来 爸爸!

615
00:56:19,670 --> 00:56:23,510
