and you tore your curtains What?
你还把窗帘扯下来了 怎么了?

622
00:56:46,400 --> 00:56:49,300
How did you get footprints on the ceiling?
你怎么把脚印搞到天花板上去的?

623
00:56:49,870 --> 00:56:51,430
This is simply too much.
这简直太过分了

624
00:56:51,540 --> 00:56:54,630
A temper tantrum of this magnitude is unacceptable.
你不可以这样胡闹

625
00:56:54,740 --> 00:56:56,470
But I wasn't having a tantrum!
可我没有在胡闹

626
00:56:56,580 --> 00:56:59,770
Then how did this happen? And the truth this time.
那么这是怎么回事? 这次你要说真话

627
00:57:00,480 --> 00:57:04,750
If I tell you the truth you still won't believe me.
我和你说真话 但你还是不会相信我

628
00:57:05,280 --> 00:57:07,050
Elizabeth, the truth.
伊丽莎白! 说真话

629
00:57:08,550 --> 00:57:11,720
I was flying. My fairy showed me how.
我在飞 我的仙子教我的

630
00:57:11,790 --> 00:57:16,230
Oh, forgoodness sake. Your make-believe fairy did this?
噢 你饶了我吧 又是你的那些虚构的仙子干的?

631
00:57:16,290 --> 00:57:18,560
You've got to stop this nonsense!
你别再这么不着调了!

632
00:57:18,630 --> 00:57:21,160
But it's not nonsense, Father. It's the truth!
我没有不着调 爸爸 这是真的!

633
00:57:21,270 --> 00:57:23,330
You have a real fairy living in your room?
在你的房间有一个真的仙子?

634
00:57:23,440 --> 00:57:25,400
