爸爸 等等!

644
00:58:01,370 --> 00:58:04,140
I know this is difficult for you to understand
我知道你很难理解

645
00:58:04,210 --> 00:58:06,840
but this is all make-believe.
但这些都是虚构的

646
00:58:06,950 --> 00:58:10,180
- No! They're real! - Elizabeth, this discuss on is over.
- 不是的! 他们是真的! - 伊丽莎白 讨论到此结束

647
00:58:11,780 --> 00:58:13,110
But Father!
可是 爸爸!

648
00:58:22,290 --> 00:58:25,130
It ... It.
这...这...

649
00:58:26,200 --> 00:58:29,790
See? I told you. Faires are real!
瞧? 我告诉你了 仙子是真实的!

650
00:58:34,140 --> 00:58:36,970
It's okay. She won't hurt you.
好了 她不会伤害你的

651
00:58:39,480 --> 00:58:42,670
It's... Well, it's extraordinary!
这... 好吧 这东西可真特别!

652
00:58:42,980 --> 00:58:45,040
